# Normalize line endings across platforms. The repository stores text as
# LF, matching ruff's `line-ending = "lf"` format config, so
# `ruff format --check` passes on the Linux CI runner regardless of the
# contributor's OS. `eol=lf` also normalizes Windows checkouts to LF,
# eliminating CRLF churn introduced by `core.autocrlf`.
* text=auto eol=lf
